  <data name="Help.Content" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>TwinShell - Help

Keyboard Shortcuts:
  Ctrl+,       - Open Settings
  Ctrl+M       - Manage Categories
  Ctrl+E       - Export Configuration
  Ctrl+I       - Import Configuration
  F1           - Show this Help
  F5           - Refresh Actions
  Esc          - Clear Search

For more information, visit the documentation.</value>
