  <data name="Help.KeyboardShortcuts.Content" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Keyboard Shortcuts:

Search &amp; Navigation:
  Tab              - Navigate between controls
  Ctrl+F           - Focus search box
  Enter            - Execute selected action
  Esc              - Clear search/filters

Actions:
  Ctrl+C           - Copy command to clipboard
  Ctrl+E           - Export configuration
  Ctrl+I           - Import configuration
  F1               - Help

Categories:
  Ctrl+M           - Manage categories

General:
  Ctrl+,           - Open settings
  Alt+F4           - Exit application</value>
